						<div class="postbody">Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade changed the background color 16 times at the title screen, but if you look closely at the screen, you'll notice that the rightmost 40 pixels are blank in scanlines where the palette changes.  It also shows some minor glitches in Nintendulator periodically.<br /><br />Also, you can't have sprites on scanlines where you change the palette.</div>

					
